# UC Talent Workflow — Parent Workspace

This rule applies to the UC Talent parent workspace.

Open Cursor from the parent folder that contains:

```txt
AGENTS.md
.cursor/
uc-talent-backend/
uc-backend-fastapi/
uc-embedding-fastapi/
uc-frontend-nextjs-v1/
uc-ats-react-app/
ucl-web/
ucl-web-cms/
```

Do not run agent sessions from a child repo unless the user explicitly wants single-repo work.

---

## 1. Workspace rule

Always use workspace-root paths.

Good:

```txt
uc-talent-backend/src/modules/...
uc-backend-fastapi/...
uc-embedding-fastapi/...
uc-frontend-nextjs-v1/...
uc-ats-react-app/...
ucl-web/...
ucl-web-cms/src/api/...
```

Avoid bare paths like:

```txt
src/...
app/...
components/...
```

unless the current working directory is already confirmed to be the target repo.

One task may touch multiple sibling repos, but only when the Jira ticket requires it.

Do not inspect or edit every repo by default.

